column8: Now hold a moment! I just can't accept such gifts and leave you empty-handed, you should know! So, I want you to have this, with my compliments!
Why, that's the finest offering I've seen all day, Nephew! You're much too kind! And likewise, so am I, as I've a little something for you, too!
You can do this, little Hades!!
Ahoy, my nephew, it is I!
It's good to see you, Nephew!
My thanks are just as boundless as the sea!
You honor your Lord Uncle, little Nephew!
I'm proud to call you nephew, little Nephew!
I'm thankful for the gesture there!
Here, look, I got you THIS!
Think you're going to like this!
Oof, now that was not on purpose...!
Not the most graceful effort there!
I warn you not to trifle with me, Nephew!
Oh you shouldn't have done that.
My tolerance has limits, little Hades.
Who do you think you are!
You cannot treat your uncle like THIS!
I'm kind of busy at this time?
I knew that you could pull it off!

I have to tell you something, little Hades: My relatives and I, we have been holding back one of our greatest gifts!! To see if you were worthy. And you are! May I present to you... the gift of pure, unbridled rage!!
Whew! I win again, haha! That Hermes, he is quick and limber as can be. But I am strong, and therefore I'm the fastest one of all!
Next time, Nephew, best not be such a fool!
You disrespect the sea, and it is liable to swallow you!
Do not forget yourself with me next time, Nephew!
It's time to make a splash!
You call for my aid, now?!
Oh, now you want my help?!
